      Become a Sponsor

    %p
      Thank you so much for your interest in becoming a sponsor of VirtKick!
    %p
      VirtKick is an open source project that will to push the envelope of virtualization sofware.<br/>
      VirtKick will make its slogan, 1-click cloud management, a reality.
    %p
      But my team needs your help to achieve that!
    %p
      I prepared a few sponsoring packages. I am sure you will find a well-suited offer for your company.<br/>
      Please note our company will issue an invoice for your payment.
    %p
      Let me know if you have any questions or suggestions - I will be happy to answer.

    %p
      Damian Nowak
      %br
      Project Lead
